# Architecture

- Web and API are separate deployable apps in one monorepo.
- UI calls backend only through `@app/api-client`.
- Shared schemas and types live in `@app/contracts`.
- Do not add duplicate layers for the same responsibility.
- Keep API routes thin; add services only when logic grows.

When unsure, read `docs/architecture.md` and `AGENTS.md`.
